    <item>
      <title>super cold (but sunny; don&#39;t forget that it was sunny)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/2015/2015-02-20-super-cold-but-sunny-dont-forget-that-it-was-sunny/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2015 00:28:00 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/2015/2015-02-20-super-cold-but-sunny-dont-forget-that-it-was-sunny/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;One of my favorite weather forecasts comes from &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.forecast.io&#34;&gt;forecast.io&lt;/a&gt;. This screen shows the ensemble set of forecasts they have for temperature for tomorrow (February 20, 2015), highlighting the 8:00 a.m. reading.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;asset-img-link&#34;  href=&#34;http://vielmetti.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4f1a53ef01b7c7508be5970b-pi&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8341c4f1a53ef01b7c7508be5970b img-responsive&#34; style=&#34;width: 600px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;&#34; alt=&#34;Screen Shot 2015-02-20 at 12.18.04 AM&#34; title=&#34;Screen Shot 2015-02-20 at 12.18.04 AM&#34; src=&#34;http://vielmetti.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4f1a53ef01b7c7508be5970b-600wi&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll note from this graph that there are several weather models they are pulling from. The one of them that has the coldest predicted weather is &lt;a href=&#34;http://weather.rap.ucar.edu/model/&#34;&gt;RAP&lt;/a&gt; from the National Center for Atmospheric Research in Boulder, Colorado. Looking at their set of pages they have a nice cold temperature forecast map. Brrr! You have to head pretty far to escape the frigid air, it looks like the vector towards warmth is to the southwest&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;asset-img-link&#34;  href=&#34;http://vielmetti.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4f1a53ef01bb07f43e96970d-pi&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8341c4f1a53ef01bb07f43e96970d img-responsive&#34; style=&#34;width: 600px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;&#34; alt=&#34;Ruc12hr_sfc_temp&#34; title=&#34;Ruc12hr_sfc_temp&#34; src=&#34;http://vielmetti.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4f1a53ef01bb07f43e96970d-600wi&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Your mileage (and temperature) may vary from the predictions.&lt;/p&gt;
